Available Tools: add_to_cart | remove_from_cart | update_quantity | get_cart | apply_coupon | checkout
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "product_id": "string", "quantity": number, "coupon_code": "string" }
Response Schema: { "cart_id": "string", "items": [{ "product_id": "string", "name": "string", "quantity": number, "price": number }], "total": number }
---
Question: Add two wireless headphones to my cart.
Call: { "func_call": "add_to_cart", "product_id": "WH-1000XM5", "quantity": 2, "coupon_code": null }
Response: { "cart_id": "cart_8923", "items": [{ "product_id": "WH-1000XM5", "name": "Sony Wireless Noise Cancelling Headphones", "quantity": 2, "price": 349.99 }], "total": 699.98 }

Question: Remove the blue t-shirt from my shopping cart.
Call: { "func_call": "remove_from_cart", "product_id": "TSH-BLU-M", "quantity": 1, "coupon_code": null }
Response: { "cart_id": "cart_8923", "items": [{ "product_id": "WH-1000XM5", "name": "Sony Wireless Noise Cancelling Headphones", "quantity": 2, "price": 349.99 }], "total": 699.98 }

